g">\r\n                <h1>\r\n                    SLIDERS CABLE PARK&apos;S FACILITIES\r\n                </h1>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="h5"></div>\r\n            <div class="para">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Sliders consists of 2 system 5:0 Olympic standard cables and 2 &apos;easy rides&apos; to teach new water sports enthusiasts. It is equipped with 11 floating plastic obstacles that enable riders to perform various tricks. All technology is produced by Rixen, a German company.\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class="h5"></div>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Also includes:\r\n                </p>\r\n                <ul>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        A swimming pool.\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        A beach volleyball area.\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        Restaurant & Bar overlooking the wonderful view.\r\n                    </li>\r\n                </ul>\r\n                <div class="h5"></div>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Occasionally Sliders turns into the hottest party zone, offering unique pool parties and unforgettable night events with famous DJs.\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class="h5"></div>\r\n                <a href="https://www.sliderscablepark.com">www.sliderscablepark.com</a>\r\n                <div class="h5"></div>\r\n                <a style="display:inline-block" href="https://www.facebook.com/ELGOUNACABLE">\r\n                    <img class="icon" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c2/F_icon.svg/2000px-F_icon.svg.png"/>\r\n                </a>\r\n<!--                    Sliders Cable Park on Facebook: \r\n                <br/>\r\n                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ELGOUNACABLE">https://www.facebook.com/ELGOUNACABLE</a>-->\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </body>\r\n</html>\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 2, 0, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 0);
