cean View\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    Diving: PADI, CMAS Barracude, Snorkeling\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    T <a href="tel:+20653580350">+20 65 358 0350</a><a href="tel:+20653580358">/8</a>\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    F <a href="fax:+20653580355">+20 65 358 0350</a><a href="tel:+20653580356">/6</a>\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    Mob <a href="tel:+201066654102">+20 106 665 41 02</a>\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    <a href="mailto:info@bluebrothersdiving.de">info@bluebrothersdiving.de</a>\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    <a href="www.bluebrothersdiving.de">www.bluebrothersdiving.de</a>\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    is produced by Rixen, a German company\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="h5"></div>\r\n            <img src="data:image/png;base64," />\r\n            <div class="h5"></div>\r\n            <div class="para">\r\n                <h3>\r\n                    Easy Divers Academy\r\n                </h3>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Location: TTC Rihana\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    Diving: FFESM, PADI, CMAS, Snorkeling, glass-bottomed boat.\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    T <a href="tel:+20653580025">+20 65 358 00(25)</a> to (29)\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    Mob <a href="tel:+201222349114">+20 12 2234 9114</a>\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="h5"></div>\r\n            <img src="data:image/png;base64," />\r\n            <div class="h5"></div>\r\n            <div class="para">\r\n                <h3>\r\n                    Colona Dive Centre\r\n                </h3>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Location: TTC Rihana\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                    Diving: PADI, snorkeling.\r\n                    <br/>\r\n                