(4, 'MÃ¶venpick Resort & Spa El Gouna', 'El Gouna', '33.813969       ', '27.252991 ', NULL, 5, 5, 1, 'Luxurious and discreet in a truly Swiss way. Each room is graced with breathtaking views of the sea, the lagoons or the hotelâ€™s lush gardens. The hotel has received several awards for efforts in regard to the environment. Housed in a privileged location, guests are only a few minutes away from the downtown and resort\'s extensive facilities of Downtown areas of  Tamr Henna and Kafr El Gouna, where shopping arcades, cafÃ©s, restaurants, and entertainment venues featuring folklore shows and live music await.', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 420\r\nClassic Rooms : 150  - Leisure Rooms 190\r\nLeisure sea view rooms: 46\r\nDeluxe lagoon view rooms: 125 Deluxe sea view rooms: 100\r\nï‚§ Deluxe Suites: 17  Family  Duplex room: 28\r\nViews: sea, lagoon, garden ,pool \r\n', '', 'www.moevenpick-hotels.com/el-gouna', '(+2 065) 354 4501, 358 0120', '', ' https://www.facebook.com/moevenpick.elgouna.resort?fref=ts&ref=br_tf', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1),
(5, 'Sheraton Miramar Resort', 'El Gouna', '33.813969', '27.252991', NULL, 10, 2, 0, 'Sheraton Miramar Resort is an oasis of peace and tranquility built on nine islands amidst lush gardens. Designed by the renowned architect Michael Graves, its architecture is an inviting mix of Arabian and Nubian style. The unique seafront setting of the resort lies against the dramatic backdrop of desert  where crystalline lagoons, wooden bridges and lush gardens give you the sensation of being in another world.', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 339\r\nSuites: 11\r\nViews: beach front, lagoon and pool\r\n', '', 'reservations.miramargouna@sheraton.com', '(+2 065) 354 5606, 358 0100/ 01 ', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/sheratonmiramarresort                      ', 'https://twitter.com/SheratonMiramar', 'https://instagram.com/sheratonmiramar/', '', '', 0, 2, 1),
(6, 'Steigenberger Golf Resort', 'El Gouna', '33.678590', '27.390670', NULL, 0, 3, 1, 'Situated amidst the golf course, this luxurious resort mixes modern architecture with a regional tradition. The lush gardens are surrounded by lagoons. Offering fine cuisine and excellent service, the hotel caters to the sophisticated golfer and vacationer. Steigenberger wellness and\r\nHealth club located at the Golf Club house features. Golfers are attracted by the year-round sunshine gracing a challenging course, couples come for the hotelâ€™s fine dining options and attentive service, and families enjoy the multitude of outdoor activities that characterize vacations in Egypt The Steigenberger Golf Resort is also a prized venue for weddings, from intimate affairs to large-scale banquets..\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 268    Standard: 141  Superior: 55 Apartments: 14 Family: 13   \r\nSuites: 45\r\nViews: golf course, pool, lagoon, garden\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 3, 1),
(7, 'Club Paradiso El Gouna', 'El Gouna', '33.682963', '27.38649 ', NULL, 0, 4, 0, 'With rooms overlooking of beachfront 100 meters from the golf course, Club Paradiso El Gouna is an all-inclusive beachfront resort built along the nicest bay of El Gouna on the Red Sea coast of Egypt. A myriad of activities, cheerful entertainment, and friendly service characterize this comfortable retreat in beautiful natural setting .Enjoy deluxe restaurants offering specialties and superb buffet. ', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 239 Club room garden view: 117 Club room pool view: 68 Club room Sea view: 40\r\nSuites: 14\r\nViews: Sea, pool, garden\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 4, 1),
(8, 'Ali Pasha', 'Abu Tig', '33.673457', '27.406404', NULL, 3.7, 3, 0, 'Ali Pasha Hotel is located in the Abu Tig Marina, one of El Gounaâ€™s liveliest areas, where guests have direct access to some of the best shopping, dining, and nightlife available. A modern oriental style sets the mood as guests enjoy Ali Pashaâ€™s private and intimate environment with individualized service. Rooms are simple but comfortable and decorated with flair. The hotelâ€™s restaurant, Tandoori, is El Gounaâ€™s only Indian specialty restaurant serving authentic North Indian cuisine; it attracts both in-house guests and clients from all over El Gouna.  Guest have access to the private marina beach.\r\n\r\nPools: 2\r\nRestaurant (Indian): 1\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 67\r\nViews: Pool, Marina\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '(+2 065) 358 0088', 'http://alipasha.elgouna.com ', 'www.facebook.com/AliPashaHotel', 'https://twitter.com/ElGounaRedSea', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial', '', 0, 1, 1),
(9, 'Arena Inn', 'Downtown', '33.675449', '27.394593', NULL, 0, 3, 0, 'Situated on the shores of a lagoon, the hotel is adjacent to the lively Downtown area with its colorful arcades, restaurants, bars and shops. The inn offers all amenity comforts of a full-service hotel. Visitors will appreciate the private swimming pool and beautifully designed restaurant overlooking the lagoon and beach. Arena Inn Hotel is within walking distance from the lively downtown area with shopping arcades, restaurants and bars. The hotel also features 33 apartments in a separate building with a private swimming pool.\r\n\r\nPools: 2 (1 adult, 1 junior) + 1 in Apartment building\r\nRestaurants & bars: 2\r\nInternal extension: 150\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 144\r\nApartments: 33\r\nViews: Lagoon, Downtown El Gouna, Golf Course\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '(+2 065) 358 0078/(+2 065) 358 0079', 'http://arenainn.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/ArenaInnElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial  ', '', 0, 3, 1),
(12, 'Ancient Sands Golf Resort & Residences', 'Abu Tig', '33.662814', '27.413325', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=67384&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 5, 0, 'If you\'re looking for a perfect escape in the sun, then the fully managed five star serviced apartments and hotel rooms at Ancient Sands Resort in El Gouna are for you. The stunning accommodations are located atop a hill with exquisite views over the Red Sea, golf course and jagged mountains and close by the beach and Abu Tig Marina. Lush landscaping surrounds the suites at Ancient Sands Resort to provide a tropical paradise amidst the desert.\r\n\r\nPools: 4 \r\nRestaurants & bars: 2\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Deluxe Rooms are available in bed and breakfast whereas all suites, villas and apartments are offered on bed only pricing.\r\nTotal rooms: 137\r\nDeluxe Rooms : 56 \r\nSuite: 31\r\nOne Bedroom apartment: 26\r\n2 bedrooms apartment: 13\r\n3 bedrooms apartment: 4\r\nTownhouse: 5\r\nGolf Villa with 2 Bedrooms: 1\r\nGolf Villa with 3 Bedrooms: 1\r\nViews: golf course, pool, sea, Court yard\r\n', '', 'fo.department@ancientsandsresort.com', '+20653545682  ', 'www.ancientsands.elgouna.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/ancientsands', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/elgounaredsea/', '', '', 0, 2, 0),
(22, 'Bellevue Beach Hotel', 'Downtown', '33.683309', '27.396598', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=65399&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 4, 0, 'Bellevue Beach Hotel is a family-oriented hotel built on the slopes of the upscale residential neighborhood of The Hill, it boasts prime beach frontage complemented by tranquil gardens planted with palm trees and flowering bushes. This mid-sized hotel offers a peaceful setting only a few minutes away from the El Kafr and Tamer Henna Downtown areas with their bustling shopping.\r\n\r\nPools: 2  + 1 kids Pool\r\nRestaurants: 1\r\nBars: 2\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 101  \r\nVillas , Junior Suites, standard rooms, sea view and sea front rooms\r\nViews: Sea, lagoon or garden\r\n', '', 'info@bellevue.elgouna.com', '+20653545161', 'http://www.bellevue.elgouna.com ', 'https://www.facebook.com/BellevueElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial  ', '', 104831, 4, 0),
(32, 'Captain’s Inn', 'Abu Tig', '33.674080', '27.408741', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28657&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 3, 0, 'A boutique guesthouse overlooking the beautiful Abu Tig Marina, captains Inn offers an intimate atmosphere in picturesque surroundings. The inn offers modern and stylish accommodation, as well as a specialty American-style Steak House restaurant on the marina\'s promenade. It\'s ideally situated in the center of the Abu Tig Marina and is hosti to he Marina Festival in the summer. Bartender Bar is the place to be for cocktails, flaring made by Ray. Captains Inn guests also have free access to the Ali Pasha swimming pool and the Marina Beach.\r\n\r\nRestaurant & bars: 2', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 50\r\nStandard: 28 \r\nSuites: 22 \r\nMarina view 16 , family rooms 2 , single rooms 2\r\nViews: marina, courtyard\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+2 065358 0170', 'http://captainsinn.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/CaptainsInnElGouna', '', 'http://instagram.com/thecaptainsinn', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial', '', 104831, 5, 0),
(42, 'La Branda Club Paradisio', 'Golf Course', '33.683993', '27.386413', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=60933&Chain=11787&template=RBE&shell=RBE&currency=EGP', 0, 4, 0, 'With rooms overlooking beachfront of 100 meters from the golf course, Labranda Club Paradiso El Gouna is an all-inclusive beachfront resort built along the nicest bay of El Gouna. A myriad of activities, cheerful entertainment, and friendly service characterize this comfortable retreat in a beautiful natural setting. Enjoy deluxe restaurants offering specialties and a superb buffet. \r\n\r\nPools: 3\r\nRestaurants & bars: 5\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 239 \r\nClub room garden view: 117 \r\nClub room pool view: 68 \r\nClub room Sea view: 70\r\nSuites: 14\r\nViews: Sea, pool, garden\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+2 065 354 7934 ', 'http://www.clubparadisio.elgouna.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/ClubParadisioHotel', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/elgounaredsea/', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial', '', 104839, 6, 0),
(52, 'Dawar El Omda ', 'Downtown', '33.676876', '27.396905', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28662&Chain=11787&currency=EGP ', 0, 4, 0, 'The architectural style of this intimate boutique hotel is reminiscent of an Upper Egyptian mayor\'s mansion. Authentic to the core, the hotel\'s architecture is complimented by superb interior design. Located in downtown El Gouna, this 4-star boutique hotel has the distinctive aspect of being partially built over a lagoon with a private beach. Local textures, mosaic floors, meticulously chosen antique furniture, original paintings and decorative elements in wrought iron and brass give Dawar its oriental flair. Free access to Zeytouna Beach equipped with umbrellas and chairs to access the Red Sea waters. Enjoy your stay in the oriental-style rooms with large windows or terraces overlooking the pool or garden.\r\n\r\nPool: 1\r\nRestaurants & bars: 4\r\n\r\nPlease note: Adults only +18 \r\n\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 66 \r\nStandard: 26\r\nLagoon/pool rooms: 37 \r\nSuites: 3\r\nViews: pool, lagoon, garden\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+2 0653580063', 'http://dawarelomda.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/Dawar.elOmda.Boutique.Hotel.ElGouna', '', '', '', '', 104836, 7, 0),
(62, 'Fanadir Hotel ', 'Abu Tig', '33.673126', '27.411462', NULL, 0, 4, 0, 'Situated in the heart of El Gounaâ€™s Abu Tig Marina North Basin on the Red Sea, the four-star Fanadir Hotel welcomes guests all year around. An Arabic inspired modern architecture and dÃ©cor with warm and comforting tones invite visitors to enjoy all that El Gouna has to offer. The hotel is committed to the green concept of El Gouna town: all rooms are equipped with power saving cards, and magnetic switches that turn off the air conditioning when windows are opened. Ideal for couples seeking a romantic escape or a relaxed place close to the nightlife and the kitesurf beach.\r\n\r\nPlease note: Adults only +18 \r\n\r\nPools: 1\r\nRestaurants & bars: 3', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 54\r\nStandard: 21       \r\nDeluxe rooms: 19\r\nSuites: 12\r\nDisabled rooms: 2\r\nViews: marina, pool, mountains\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '(+2 065) 3580076', 'http://fanadir.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/FanadirHotelElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial     ', '', 104841, 8, 1),
(72, 'La Maison Bleue', 'Abu Tig', '33.670299', '27.422547', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=62615&Chain=11787&adult=2&child=0&template=RBE&shell=RBE&currency=EGP', 4.3, 6, 0, 'La Maison Bleue is a luxury guesthouse set directly on the northern shores of Mangroovy Beach and its kitesurfing stations, it offers seclusion as well as easy access to the town\'s facilities. The restaurants, bars, boutiques, and street festivals of Abu Tig Marina are in close proximity, and the Downtown shopping and dining venues are a few kilometers away. La Maison Bleue caters to a clientele accustomed to the excellence of luxury hotels. Couples can rely on flawless organization to celebrate special occasions, while celebrities can rest assured that their privacy will be respected. Evoking the grandeur of olden times while offering all the modern amenities, La Maison Bleue transports you into a different world yet makes you feel right at home.\r\n\r\nPools: 1 heated in the winter time\r\nRestaurants: 1\r\nBars: 1\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 10 \r\nViews: Sea, pool\r\n', '', 'front.office@lamaison-bleue.com', '+20653545604', 'http://www.mosaique.elgouna.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/LaMaisonBleue.ElGouna?fref=ts', '', 'https://www.instagram.com/lamaisonbleue_elgouna/ ', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial     ', '', 0, 9, 0),
(82, 'Mövenpick Resort & Spa ', 'Downtown', '33.684478', '27.395668', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28683&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 5, 0, 'Luxurious and discreet in a truly Swiss way. Each room is graced with breathtaking views of the sea, the lagoons or the hotel\'s lush gardens. The hotel has received several awards for efforts in regard to the environment. Housed in a privileged location, guests are only a few minutes away from the downtown areas of Tamr Henna and Kafr El Gouna, where shopping arcades, cafe, restaurants, and entertainment venues featuring folklore shows and live music await.\r\n\r\nPools: 3 + 2 children\'s pools\r\nRestaurants & bars: 4 restaurants, 2 pool restaurants &Bar, 1 Bar \r\nConference capacity: 500\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total Rooms : 420 \r\nClassic Rooms Garden View:             150\r\nDeluxe Lagoon View:                        125\r\nDeluxe Sea View:                              100\r\nFamily Duplex:                                   28\r\nDeluxe Suites:                                    15\r\nFamily Deluxe Suite:                           1 \r\nPresidential Suite:                               1\r\nViews: sea, lagoon, garden, pool \r\n', '', 'reservation.elgouna@moevenpick.com', '+20653544501', 'www.moevenpick-hotels.com/el-gouna', 'https://www.facebook.com/moevenpick.elgouna.resort?fref=ts&ref=br_tf', '', '', '', '', 0, 10, 0),
(92, 'Mosaique ', 'Abu Tig', '33.672688', '27.412377', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=29572&Chain=11787&currency=EGP ', 0, 4, 0, 'The four-star Kite & Surf Mosaique Hotel is located in the heart of Abu Tig Marina North Basin in El Gouna. Arabesque style architecture with a Moroccan flair and cool decor provide a relaxing atmosphere for guests. All the rooms are surrounding the pool area and offer either Pool view or Marina view. The rooms are spacious and all have a private terrace/balcony -- some with direct pool-access. Guests can relax in the Hood which host weekly movie nights or the pool terrace bar.\r\n\r\nPools: 2 (1 adult, 1 children)\r\nRestaurants & bars: 3\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 69  \r\nStandard: 33  \r\nDeluxe rooms: 26 \r\nSuites: 8\r\nDisabled rooms: 2\r\nViews: marina, pool \r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+20653580077', 'http://mosaique.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/MosaiqueHotelElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial ', '', 114188, 11, 0),
(102, 'Sheraton Miramar Resort', 'TU Berlin Campus El Gouna', '33.677731', '27.405444', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28682&Chain=11787&adult=2&child=0&template=RBE&shell=RBE&currency=EGP', 0, 5, 0, 'Sheraton Miramar Resort is an oasis of peace and tranquility built on nine islands amidst lush gardens. Designed by the renowned architect Michael Graves, its architecture is an inviting mix of Arabian and Nubian style. The unique seafront setting of the resort lies against the dramatic backdrop of desert where crystalline lagoons, wooden bridges and lush gardens give you the sensation of being in another world.\r\n\r\nPools: 5 (2 adult, 3 child)\r\nRestaurants & bars: 9\r\nConference capacity: 250\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 339\r\nSuites: 11\r\nViews: beach front, lagoon and pool\r\n', '', 'Miramargouna@sheraton.com', '+2 0653545606', 'http://www.sheratonmiramarresort.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/sheratonmiramarresort ', 'https://twitter.com/SheratonMiramar', 'https://www.instagram.com/sheratonmiramar/', '', '', 0, 12, 0),
(112, 'Steigenberger Golf Resort', 'Golf Course', '33.678064', '27.390531', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28781&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 5, 0, 'Situated amidst the golf course, this luxurious resort mixes modern architecture with a regional tradition. The hotel is walking distance to Club Paradisio beach and facilities. It is surrounded by lagoons and golf greeneries. Golfers are attracted by the year-round sunshine gracing the challenging course, couples come for the hotel\'s fine dining options and attentive service, and families enjoy the multitude of outdoor activities that characterize vacations in El Gouna and Egypt. The Steigenberger Golf Resort is also a prized venue for weddings, from intimate affairs to large-scale banquets.\r\n\r\nPools: 2 adult, 2 Junior \r\nRestaurants & bars: 7\r\nConference room capacity: 100\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 268    Standard: 141  Superior: 55 Apartments: 14 Family: 13   \r\nSuites: 45\r\nViews: golf course, pool, lagoon, garden\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+20653580140', 'www.steigenbergergolfelgouna.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/SteigenbergerGolfResortElGouna/?fref=ts', '', '', '', '', 104832, 13, 0),
(122, 'Sultan Bey ', 'Downtown', '33.679128', '27.397611', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=29116&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 4, 0, 'Sultan Bey is a labyrinth of alleyways, courtyards and domes that spread from the shores of the turquoise lagoons to the heart of downtown El Gouna. This four-star hotel prides itself on providing guests with service of the highest standard in intimate surroundings. Enjoy beautifully decorated rooms complete with balconies or terraces with views of the lagoon or central courtyard. Guests will have free access to Zeytouna Beach.\r\n\r\nPool: 1 for Adult & 1 for children \r\nRestaurants & bars: 4\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 115\r\nViews: courtyard, lagoon pool ', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+20653545600', 'http://sultanbey.elgouna.com', 'www.facebook.com/SultanBeyhotelElGouna', '', '', '', '', 104833, 14, 0),
(132, 'The Three Corners Ocean View ', 'Abu Tig', '33.677851', '27.407558', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28667&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 4, 0, 'The Three Corners Ocean View Hotel offers travelers a much sought-after address: the Abu Tig Marina. Just a short walk from El Gouna\'s most exclusive shopping and dining experience, the hotel enjoys well-appointed rooms with fabulous views and a stunning pool overlooking the sea. The Three Corners Ocean View Hotel offers a 4-star all-inclusive experience in an adult-only environment.\r\n\r\nPlease note: Adults only +16\r\n\r\nPools: 2 (2 adult)\r\nRestaurants & bars: 7\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 157\r\nViews: sea, pool, garden\r\n', '', 'res-oceanview@threecorners.com', '+2 0653580350  ', 'info@threecorners.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/TheThreeCornersOceanViewHotel', '', '', '', '', 0, 15, 0),
(142, 'The Three Corners Rihana Inn', 'TU Berlin Campus El Gouna', '33.672778', '27.399806', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28669&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 4, 0, 'The Three Corners Rihana Inn is built in a Nubian style with traditional domes and arches in warm sunset colours. The hotel offers maximum comfort for couples and families with both standard and connected rooms. Rihana Inn guests have full access to Rihanna Resort with its variety of facilities and a private sandy beach on the lagoon. \r\n\r\nPools: 6 (3, each with integrated kid pool and 2 aqua park pools)\r\nRestaurants/bars: 10\r\nConference capacity: 60\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 166\r\nStandard: 47\r\nConnected: 112\r\nViews: pool, mountain, garden\r\n', '', 'res-rihana@threecorners.com', '+20653580029', 'info@threecorners.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/The-Three-Corners-Rihana-Resort-Inn-161953207159840/', '', '', '', '', 0, 16, 0),
(152, 'The Three Corners Rihanna Resort', 'TU Berlin Campus El Gouna', '33.672474', '27.399335', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28665&Chain=11787 &currency=EGP ', 0, 4, 0, 'Built along the banks of a private El Gouna lagoon, The Three Corners Rihana Resort is a Nubian style architectural masterpiece, featuring clusters of buildings with typical domes and arches in warm sunset colors, complimented by lush, landscaped gardens.\r\nWith its newly added Aquapark, featuring 2 pools, slides and aqua games (coming soon), the Three Corners Rihanna Resort is particularly suited for families and groups of friends, but also for singles and couples.\r\n\r\nPools: 6 (3, each with an integrated kids pool)and 2 aquapark pools\r\nRestaurants & bars: 11\r\nConference capacity: 60\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 268\r\nStandard: 142   \r\nSuperior: 82\r\nConnected: 30\r\nHandicapped accessible: 14\r\nViews: garden, lagoon, mountain, pools \r\n', '', 'res-rihana@threecorners.com', '+20653580029', 'info@threecorners.com', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Three-Corners-Rihana-Resort/161953207159840', '', '', '', '', 0, 17, 0),
(162, 'Turtle’s Inn', 'Abu Tig', '33.674063', '27.408004', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28661&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 3, 0, 'Bold colours, refreshing style and personalized service welcome guests at this quaint hotel. With excellent location and beautiful views, Turtles Inn is a small intimate 3 star guesthouse located in the heart of the famous Abu Tig Marina in El Gouna, with access to many restaurants, bars and upscale boutiques. A small pool gives you a chance to refresh or follow a diving course with the in house diving center. A gastronomical Belgian restaurant is housed on the roof top terrace. Free access to Marina beach and Ali Pasha swimming pools.\r\n\r\nPool: 1\r\nRestaurant & bars: 1\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 28\r\nViews: marina, pool\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+20653580171', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/TurtlesInnElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial  ', '', 104837, 18, 0),
(172, 'Ali Pasha ', 'Abu Tig', '33.673924', '27.406480', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28658&Chain=11787&currency=EGP', 0, 3, 0, 'Ali Pasha Hotel is located in the Abu Tig Marina, one of El Gouna\'s liveliest areas, where guests have direct access to some of the best shopping, dining, and nightlife available. A modern oriental style sets the mood as guests enjoy Ali Pasha\'s private and intimate environment with individualized service. Rooms are simple but comfortable and decorated with flair. The hotel\'s restaurant, Tandoori, is El Gouna\'s only Indian specialty restaurant serving authentic North Indian cuisine; it attracts both in-house guests and clients from all over El Gouna.  Guest have access to the private marina beach.\r\n\r\nPools: 2\r\nRestaurant (Indian): 1\r\n', 'Offer', '1) Free Drinks\r\n2) free wifi', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 67  \r\nViews: pool, marina\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', ' +2 065358 0088', 'http://alipasha.elgouna.com ', 'www.facebook.com/AliPashaHotel', 'https://twitter.com/ElGounaRedSea', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial  ', '', 104838, 20, 0),
(182, 'Arena Inn', 'Downtown', '33.675506', '27.394240', 'https://gc.synxis.com/rez.aspx?Hotel=28660&Chain=11787 &currency=EGP', 0, 3, 0, 'Situated on the shores of a lagoon, the hotel is adjacent to the lively Downtown area with its colorful arcades, restaurants, bars and shops. Visitors will appreciate the private swimming pool and friendliness of the staff. The Arena Inn Hotel is a bed and breakfast only hotel, offering a dining passport to restaurants around El Gouna. The hotel also features 33 apartments in a separate building with a private swimming pool.\r\n\r\nPools: 2 (1 adult, 1 junior) + 1 in Apartment building\r\nRestaurants & bars: 2\r\n', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Total rooms: 144\r\nApartments: 33\r\nViews: Lagoon, Downtown El Gouna, Golf Course\r\n', '', 'reservations@elgouna.com', '+2 0653580078', '', 'www.facebook.com/ArenaInnElGouna', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/user/ELGOUNAofficial  ', '', 104834, 32, 0),
